{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To connect VigramSDK in this example we will use ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.swift.org\/package-manager\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"We also recommend using this method instead of CocoaPods.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Step 1. Add Package Dependencies in your project.","anchor":"Step-1-Add-Package-Dependencies-in-your-project"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To add a framework to your project, you need to select Add Package Dependencies in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"File","type":"text"}]},{"text":" section of the top menu of Xcode:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig1.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Paste into the search bar url:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["https:\/\/github.com\/vigram-sw\/SDK_iOS_viDoc_Distribution.git"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig2.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After entering the address, the SDK name, the current release version, and the project to which the library will be added will appear:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig3.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Make sure you have access to an internet connection and that the project you are adding the framework to is selected correctly","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Also pay attention to the release version indicated in the window. The version number can be changed manually.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The actual release version is always indicated on the main page of this guide.","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After this, you need to click on the Add Package button:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig4.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After this, the process of checking and unpacking the library will begin. Wait until it is finished:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig5.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Select your project:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig6.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Once you add the project, the dependency will appear in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Package Dependencies","type":"text"}]},{"text":" section of your project. Again, pay attention to the library version:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig7.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Try building the project. To do this, select the Build command in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Product","type":"text"}]},{"text":" section or run the command using hotkeys (","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"command + b","type":"text"}]},{"text":")","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig8.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the project builds successfully, all actions have been performed correctly.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Step 2. Import library","anchor":"Step-2-Import-library"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To use VigramSDK tools you need to import framework into your class:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["import VigramSDK"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"fig9.png","type":"image"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This completes the framework import procedure.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The next step is ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitle":"to authenticate the SDK.","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/Step2SDKAuthentication","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"to authenticate the SDK."}],"type":"reference"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"*All methods and functions specified in this manual are also available in the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/vigram-sw\/SDK_iOS_viDoc_Distribution\/tree\/demo\/","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Navigation","anchor":"Navigation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"Up to Getting started with VigramSDK","type":"text"}],"overridingTitle":"Up to Getting started with VigramSDK","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/GettingStarted","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"✅ ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"STEP 1 (Import VigramSDK)","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"STEP 2 (SDK Authentication)","type":"text"}],"overridingTitle":"STEP 2 (SDK Authentication)","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/Step2SDKAuthentication","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"STEP 3 (Description of configuration parameters)","type":"text"}],"overridingTitle":"STEP 3 (Description of configuration parameters)","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/Step3ConfigurationParameters","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridin